import React, {Component} from 'react';
import {Form, FormGroup, Label, Input, Container, Row, Col} from "reactstrap";

class Search extends Component {
    render(){
        return <Container>
            <Row>
                <Col md="12">
                    <Form>
                        <FormGroup>
                            <Label for="pokemon"
                            >
                                Pokemon a buscar: 
                                </Label>
                            <Input type="text" 
                            name="pokemon" 
                            placeholder="Nombre de pokemon" 
                            />
                        </FormGroup>
                    </Form>
                </Col>
            </Row>
        </Container>
    }
}

export default Search
